7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Requirements of Food Safety Certification in Dubai"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:39+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"ISO 22000 Food Safety Management System (FSMS) certificate is the most sought ISO certification around the globe. Check out the requirements for successful"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Requirements of Food Safety Certification in Dubai"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 22000 is the international standard for Food Safety Management System (FSMS) which many food chain companies strive hard to get this certification. Acquiring ISO 22000 FSMS certificate is beneficial for an organization in many ways. And most importantly, having this ISO certificate will win you the customer's trust and make them think you offer safe food and ingredients of the food that are processed are safe enough to consume. Demand for ISO 22000 Certification is increasing every day and every food chain organization is anticipating getting one for them."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Unlike other food safety management certification such as FSSC and SQF, ISO 22000 FSMS certificate doesn't have specific requirements. However, we have come up with the key elements and practices for the successful acquisition of ISO 22000 certificate for any food chain organization."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Key elements for acquiring ISO 22000 FSMS certification in Dubai"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"1. Guided by Managerial Team"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Implementing Food Safety Management System is not same as the Quality management system. It is a top-management issue. Food safety should be guided and looked after by the top management team or candidates. ISO 22000 FSMS implementation mainly focuses and requires the involvement of the management team."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"2. Communication"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Since the food safety could be introduced at any stage, the clear and interactive communication within the organization or team is the key element for the successful acquisition of ISO certification for your organization. The communication within both upstream and downstream is quite significant. This will avoid miscommunications and misunderstandings. And eventually, it will minimize the risks and confusions."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"3. HACCP Principle (Hazard Analysis & Critical Control Point)"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Devising HACCP analysis will help you determine the potential hazards and give the best solution to control those hazards at specific points amidst the process. This will sort out the potential hazards in all departments such as biological, physical and chemical hazards. HACCP principle will determine the best strategy and prerequisite programmes to set up an action plan."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e","$L1f"]}],"$L20"]}]}]
